response.overview: A rare look into the life of Hollywood Legend, Dick Van Dyke. Follow Mr. Van Dyke's return to his hometown of Danville, IL as he tours the city and visits his recently condemned childhood home for the first time in over 60 years. Hear stories about his youth, Walt Disney, the efforts to save his home and so much more. Dick may be 91, but his childlike wonder and charm has not even begun to fade.
response.title: Welcome Home, Dick Van Dyke!
